<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %> | LearnHub</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      /* ---------- GLOBAL STYLES ---------- */
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      }

      body {
        background: #f8fafc;
        color: #0f172a;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 1280px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 2rem;
      }

      /* ---------- NAVBAR (same as home/courses/about) ---------- */
      .navbar {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 1000;
        padding: 1rem 0;
      }

      .nav-container {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #0f172a;
        transition: color 0.3s;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover {
        color: #2563eb;
      }

      .nav-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .btn-outline {
        padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
        border: 2px solid #2563eb;
        border-radius: 40px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #2563eb;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: 0.3s;
      }

      .btn-outline:hover {
        background: #2563eb;
        color: white;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed);
        color: white;
        border-radius: 40px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px -8px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
        transition: 0.3s;
      }

      .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 25px -8px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.5);
      }

      .mobile-menu-icon {
        display: none;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .nav-links,
        .nav-actions {
          display: none;
          width: 100%;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 1rem;
          margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .nav-links.active,
        .nav-actions.active {
          display: flex;
        }
        .mobile-menu-icon {
          display: block;
        }
      }

      /* ---------- COURSE DETAIL PAGE STYLES ---------- */
      .detail-section {
        padding: 4rem 0;
      }

      .back-link {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        display: inline-block;
        color: #2563eb;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .back-link i {
        margin-right: 0.5rem;
      }

      .course-detail-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 40px;
        padding: 3rem;
        box-shadow: 0 30px 60px -20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      .course-detail-header {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .course-icon {
        width: 100px;
        height: 100px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed);
        border-radius: 30px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: white;
        font-size: 3rem;
      }

      .course-detail-header h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .detail-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .detail-info p {
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #334155;
      }

      .detail-meta {
        background: #f1f5f9;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 30px;
      }

      .meta-item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 1rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      }

      .meta-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .meta-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #0f172a;
      }

      .meta-value {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #2563eb;
      }

      .btn-enroll {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 1rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 60px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        transition: 0.3s;
      }

      .btn-enroll:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 15px 30px -8px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.5);
      }

      .btn-back {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
        background: white;
        border: 2px solid #2563eb;
        color: #2563eb;
        border-radius: 60px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: 0.3s;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .btn-back:hover {
        background: #2563eb;
        color: white;
      }

      /* ---------- FOOTER (same as home/courses/about) ---------- */
      .footer {
        background: #0f172a;
        color: #cbd5e1;
        padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
      }

      .footer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .footer-col h4 {
        color: white;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .footer-col ul {
        list-style: none;
      }

      .footer-col ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .footer-col a {
        color: #cbd5e1;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 0.3s;
      }

      .footer-col a:hover {
        color: white;
      }

      .social-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .social-links a {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .footer-bottom {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 3rem;
        padding-top: 2rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #334155;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Include Navbar Partial -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <!-- Course Details Section -->
    <section class="detail-section">
      <div class="container">
        <a href="/courses" class="back-link">
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Courses
        </a>
        <div class="course-detail-card">
          <div class="course-detail-header">
            <div class="course-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i>
            </div>
            <h1><%= course.name %></h1>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-grid">
            <div class="detail-info">
              <h2>About this course</h2>
              <p>
                This comprehensive <strong><%= course.name %></strong> program
                is designed to take you from beginner to proficient. You'll
                learn industry best practices, work on real-world projects, and
                gain hands-on experience. The curriculum covers everything you
                need to start a successful career in tech.
              </p>
              <p>
                Duration: <strong><%= course.duration %></strong><br />
                Fees: <strong>₹<%= course.fees.toLocaleString() %></strong
                ><br />
                Mode: Online / Self-paced<br />
                Certificate: Yes
              </p>
              <h3>What you'll learn</h3>
              <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 2">
                <li>Fundamentals and advanced concepts</li>
                <li>Building real-world applications</li>
                <li>Industry best practices</li>
                <li>Deployment and scaling</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-meta">
              <div class="meta-item">
                <span class="meta-label">Course ID</span>
                <span class="meta-value"><%= course.id %></span>
              </div>
              <div class="meta-item">
                <span class="meta-label">Duration</span>
                <span class="meta-value"><%= course.duration %></span>
              </div>
              <div class="meta-item">
                <span class="meta-label">Fees</span>
                <span class="meta-value"
                  >₹<%= course.fees.toLocaleString() %></span
                >
              </div>
              <div class="meta-item">
                <span class="meta-label">Level</span>
                <span class="meta-value">Beginner to Advanced</span>
              </div>
              <div class="meta-item">
                <span class="meta-label">Language</span>
                <span class="meta-value">English</span>
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="btn-enroll">Enroll Now</a>
              <a href="/courses" class="btn-back">Browse More Courses</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Include Footer Partial -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
